metadata.name: Cyberpunk & Love
metadata.description:
It's the work I made for the Jetlag Weekly contest on this topic. 

It is a cyberpunk and love scene where both have been searching for each other unsuccessfully, going through hardships and suffering every day, until one night, thanks to the clues, which they have been following for so long, led them both to the same place and at the same time.

PNG 2000*3000 px
